entries.femaleVariant: Five years, I been giving it my all. Five years and nothing, while that bitch got bumped twice already.
You got two options. Either accept the status quo, or take out the competition.
You mean I gotta... shoot her?
Wouldn't be the worst idea. You'd show 'em you'll do anything, follow any order.
Nah, too much of a coward for that. I went status quo, made sure they saw me as no threat.
